'''ESIC Business & Marketing School''' was created in 1965 by the religious congregation [[Priests of the Sacred Heart|Priests of the Sacred Heart of Jesus]] to train the best business professionals. It was the first business school created in [[Spain]] for professionals in need to improve their training in the area of Marketing.<ref name="esic">{{cite web|url=http://www.esic.edu/institution/history/|title=History &#124; ESIC|publisher=esic.edu|accessdate=2015-05-10}}</ref><ref name="topmba">{{cite web|url=http://www.topmba.com/institution/esic-business-and-marketing-school|title=ESIC Business and Marketing School &#124; TopMBA.com|publisher=topmba.com|accessdate=2015-05-10}}</ref>
It has more than 32,000 alumni students and covers different areas of education, such as University Degrees, Master and Postgraduate Courses and Executive Education.<ref name="esic"/>
